gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Lakers 129, Thunder 120
gameRecap.excerpt: LeBron James records his 75th 40-point game of his career as the Lakers defeat the Thunder, 129-120. James recorded 40 points, seven rebounds, seven assists and five 3PM, while Anthony Davis added 26 points, 11 rebounds and seven assists for the Lakers in the victory. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander tallied 34 points, five rebounds and seven assists for the Thunder in the losing effort. The Lakers snap a 4-game losing streak as they improve to 16-14 on the season, while the Thunder fall to 18-9.
